          <td class="post-content">
            <div class="post-content-inner">
              
              Things that are irritating: enrollment periods that only last two weeks, with clearly-defined times when you can and can't make changes.<br /><br />I have no problem with the concept of making choices that'll last for a year (unless you get married or something). I have a problem with putting together the whole basket of choices, getting that information out to people, and then telling them they can't make their selections until Monday. Not just Monday, but Monday morning after 9am. As if software and the Internet have working hours.<br /><br />So stupid.

              

              
              
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
        
